      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready to enjoy the drive in this fantastic, well-maintained vehicle! It is in good condition, offering a smooth and reliable performance that you can count on. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing the care this car has received over the years\u2014it's a perfect choice for anyone looking for a dependable and stylish ride!",
