    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it's officially time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning, mint condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've pampered it since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the dealership headache, you've found it. I'd love for you to come by and see just how clean it is for yourself!",
