    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction and chassis balance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This example features documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul, ensuring the valvetrain operates with factory-spec precision. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, eliminating the common structural fatigue points associated with this platform. Power is transferred via a tactile six-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The suspension remains taut, utilizing original geometry with refreshed bushings to maintain the sharp turn-in the M-division is known for. The exterior retains its factory depth and clarity, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous mechanical stewardship.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
